{"tid":2249681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Gym room係咪有人問你就一定要同人share同一部機？","createTime":"2020-10-19T13:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T13:39:23.000Z","uid":49285,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58241a23049c22f6451eb7340fba34c58c2d4eef","tid":2249681,"uid":49285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:16:57.000Z","msg":"講真 如果未有武肺之前 有人問可唔可以share 就一定ok既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家武肺咁嚴重 我又唔知你有無病 點解要同你share先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做之前我專登晒成分鐘用酒精噴過晒個手把 坐墊 同挨pan 連較重量果粒野都噴埋抹乾淨先做<br />\n點解要同你share？唔通你做完我又要重新抹多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n做拉背Lat pull down果d都算 有時leg day做腳成個大脾出晒汗掂住塊墊 又要同你輪住做 唔會好污糟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得肯同你share做係人情 唔肯就道理 就算你有禮貌問我都會有禮貌地婉拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 絲打 每次做都係5－8set 每set10下 最多做同一部機10－12分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦唔會坐係度撳電話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主有道理 而家疫情咁嚴重 都係做完晒先俾下家做衛生D好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輪流share做係gym room潛規則 樓主唔可以咁自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454187a03591f61a04cac9f6c1df22c49e0f9cb","tid":2249681,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"好想奶你啲汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa43f0763728f551ac3ec95d4fa4326be8c132ea","tid":2249681,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"你做完俾我奶下部機就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好俾第個用左先"},{"pid":"f594c678c553f8e05a9594a134d9e5cc0ba20333","tid":2249681,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10